metadata.name: Misty
metadata.description:
Misty by Brandon Yoshizawa

Edition size: 20

A cloud inversion creeps through the valley floor in Yosemite National Park. The low fog winds its way through the trees creating an S like pattern. A magical morning in my favorite National Park.
